MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-1722. State ex rel. Apanovich v. Tubbs Jones.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. On October 10, 1995, relator filed an application for dismissal of this cause. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, nunc pro tunc, that relator’s application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective October 10,1995.
